    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a quest to defeat Fenrir. Travel distant lands, flanked by your allies, and take your rightful place by Odin's side!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Odin’s Defense is a twist on the traditional Tower Defense genre: instead of upgrades, equip your towers with powerful items to create unique effects each round. Immerse yourself in the story and make choices that will shape the outcome of your campaign. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/e63f4e74ac72a7227ea345e81934cd2d.avif?t=1762011932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras_big/e63f4e74ac72a7227ea345e81934cd2d.avif?t=1762011932 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand select the towers you will bring into battle. </strong>Get tactical, pick your favourites and charge into battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/f50ceef9f49e4f0d331ce1d36ec235e4.poster.avif?t=1762011932\" width=672 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/f50ceef9f49e4f0d331ce1d36ec235e4.webm?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/f50ceef9f49e4f0d331ce1d36ec235e4.mp4?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/9ec87a2033ecd0cbc62749052b1ebdc1.avif?t=1762011932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras_big/9ec87a2033ecd0cbc62749052b1ebdc1.avif?t=1762011932 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Spindlewood, Dunes Eternal and the Boolevard of Broken Bones await the arrival of the Bifrost!</strong> Journey across forests, graveyards, deserts and more on your quest to defeat Fenrir.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/e05b2b9c1624ddf880bef68d09ed1070.poster.avif?t=1762011932\" width=672 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/e05b2b9c1624ddf880bef68d09ed1070.webm?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/e05b2b9c1624ddf880bef68d09ed1070.mp4?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/360cce6115b75e7796a4541e9de71273.avif?t=1762011932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras_big/360cce6115b75e7796a4541e9de71273.avif?t=1762011932 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Equip your towers with powerful artefacts for support, power, extra damage and everything in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/1bacf67eacc09fde53780516671c1b88.poster.avif?t=1762011932\" width=672 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/1bacf67eacc09fde53780516671c1b88.webm?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/1bacf67eacc09fde53780516671c1b88.mp4?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/fb695536a36c892254df32d7e0f54276.avif?t=1762011932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras_big/fb695536a36c892254df32d7e0f54276.avif?t=1762011932 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destroy hoarde after hoarde of enemies in Odin's name! </strong>From slimes to gravekeepers, from spiders to mummies, there's no shortage of baddies for you to best.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/dbc799a749ee44631015d0f5d37c48f1.poster.avif?t=1762011932\" width=672 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/dbc799a749ee44631015d0f5d37c48f1.webm?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021780/extras/dbc799a749ee44631015d0f5d37c48f1.mp4?t=1762011932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Single player tower defense inspired by <strong>Norse mythology.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Traverse <strong>3 biomes</strong> on your quest to bind Fenrir. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>10 available towers</strong> all with unique abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Tons of enemies</strong> to challenge your skills and test your wits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>12 items</strong> for you to collect and use in creative ways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>The Longhouse Codex</strong>: complete in-game lore and game statistics at your fingertips. </p>",
